# Fisher itself and fisher-installed plugin files all land here because
# ~/.config/fish/functions is symlinked to this directory. They're regenerated
# by `fisher install`/`fisher update`, so track the plugin list (../fish_plugins)
# rather than the installed files. Add a line per plugin file as plugins change.
# (git never ignores already-tracked files, so your own functions are unaffected.)
fisher.fish
bass.fish
__bass.py
